snippet.title: Chaos Dynasty Honey SAGE 2021 Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! I made a Sonic fan game over the summer, called Chaos Dynasty Honey, for SAGE 2021, the Sonic Amateur Games Expo! Even though the game's been out for a few days, I wanted to put a trailer for it on my channel while the event is running. This trailer will be unlisted after SAGE 2021 has ended, however you can still play the Alpha Demo as you like!

Monthly uploads will be resuming shortly, following more information in an upcoming Tallest Flash Direct next month, where plans for the channel, new content, and development updates on Chaos Dynasty Honey, and more will be revealed!

Download the demo here: https://www.sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/chaos-dynasty-honey-sage-21-demo.1110/

___________________________________________________________________________

◤Tallest Flash Intro Music◢: 
"Critical Hit" by MDK
http://www.youtube.com/MDKOfficialYT
http://www.mdkofficial.bandcamp.com/ http://www.morgandavidking.com/free-downloads
